snippet.title: There's absolutely nothing funnier than cats - Funny cat compilation
snippet.description:
Cats and kittens are so funny and cute animals, they are simply the best! Just look how all these cats & kittens play, fail, get along with dogs, get their heads stuck, react to mirrors, make funny sounds, get angry,... So ridiculous and funny! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
